iable de type Delta Scuti">Type Delta Scuti</a> <span style="font-weight:bold">·</span></span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/%C3%89toile_variable_de_type_FU_Orionis" title="Étoile variable de type FU Orionis">Type FU Orionis</a> <span style="font-weight:bold">·</span></span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/%C3%89toile_variable_de_type_Mira" title="Étoile variable de type Mira">Type Mira</a> <span style="font-weight:bold">·</span></span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/%C3%89toile_variable_de_type_RR_Lyrae" title="Étoile variable de type RR Lyrae">Type RR Lyrae</a> <span style="font-weight:bold">·</span></span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/%C3%89toile_variable_de_type_T_Tauri" title="Étoile variable de type T Tauri">Type T Tauri</a> <span style="font-weight:bold">·</span></span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/%C3%89toile_variable_de_type_W_Virginis" title="Étoile variable de type W Virginis">Type W Virginis</a> <span style="font-weight:bold">·</span></span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/%C3%89toile_Wolf-Rayet" title="Étoile Wolf-Rayet">Wolf-Rayet</a> <span style="font-weight:bold">·</span></span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Sursauteur_gamma_mou" title="Sursauteur gamma mou">Sursauteur gamma mou</a> <span style="font-weight:bold">·</span></span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Naine_blanche_%C3%A0_pulsations" title="Naine blanche à pulsations">Blanche à pulsations</a></span></td>
